<paragraph blockId="98.[151,1437,152,487]" pageId="98" pageNumber="99">
<emphasis box="[151,233,153,178]" italics="true" pageId="98" pageNumber="99">Leaves</emphasis>
irregularly pinnate (sometimes with 1-veined pinnae present), not plicate; rachis 40.0(13.0–59.0) cm long; pinnae 4(2–12) per side of rachis; basal pinna 7.5(1.9–22.0) cm wide, forming an angle of 40(20–60)° with the rachis. 
<emphasis box="[338,506,229,255]" italics="true" pageId="98" pageNumber="99">Inflorescences</emphasis>
rachillae 18(5–39).
</paragraph>
